  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ⅢXのライブ終了後",
      "startTime": 1.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、ファッションショーを見ていた方から\n新しく仕事をもらえるなんて……",
      "startTime": 5.7999999683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "知り合いが紹介してくれたんです。ついでに新曲の\n衣装を着たプロモ用の写真を撮ってもらえるみたいで",
      "startTime": 11.8666662534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3666660786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、なんでも頼んでみるものですね\nお願いするだけならタダですから",
      "startTime": 18.7999995868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも大成功したし、バッグも無事に戻ってきたし！\nいいことって重なるものですね",
      "startTime": 25.9666652362,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.6680653999965,
          "startTime": 32.6333333016
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.433331728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、知り合いが呼んでる\nそれじゃあ、行ってきますね",
      "startTime": 30.6333319028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "『こういうポーズで……うん、通訳ありがとう\n表情は、そうね……』",
      "startTime": 41.0333322843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "『普段の撮影より、場所も衣装も派手だから\n空気感に合わせるようにするわね』",
      "startTime": 46.9666696866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "カジノを楽しみにやって来る人達を\n引きつける表情と仕草を意識して……",
      "startTime": 51.7333345731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（普段の撮影とは雰囲気から何からまるで違うのに）\n（しっかりと自分を出してる）",
      "startTime": 59.5666681607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（どんな場所でも自分の武器をしっかり）\n（見せつける……franさんの本領発揮だな）",
      "startTime": 64.5333345731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.6288844268
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.6288844268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、ファッションショーだけじゃなくて\n撮影のギャラまでその場でもらえるなんて",
      "startTime": 73.9333391507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "本当にちょうど良かったわね。このギャラを\n元手にすれば、ギャンブルなんかより確実に……",
      "startTime": 79.9666724841,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.664632099994,
          "startTime": 86.6333371162
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.8666704495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？\n知り合いのカミーユさんと連絡してるんですか？",
      "startTime": 87.4666704495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.6333338897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、さっきカジノで知り合った\n海外のセレブと連絡を取ってるんです",
      "startTime": 92.8000037829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを凄く気に入ってくれたみたいで……\n「そんなあなたにいい投資の話がある」ですって！",
      "startTime": 98.4999997139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.5333288034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "startTime": 102.5333288034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "AI関連の事業投資らしいんですけど\n話を聞けば聞くほど将来性しか見えないなって",
      "startTime": 106.3333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1666601022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "「確実に儲かるから、今の内に出来るだけ沢山の\n金額を投資した方がいい」って言われてるんです",
      "startTime": 113.6333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0666601022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "利回りも凄く良くて……\n配当を毎月支払ってくれるんですって！",
      "startTime": 119.2333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……やめておいた方がいいと思います",
      "startTime": 122.3999898751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.9999852975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。ど、どうしてですか！？",
      "startTime": 126.9999852975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんから、芸能界での似たような話は\n山ほど聞いてきましたよ",
      "startTime": 132.9333232562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺自身、星見プロが東京に来てからはそういう話を\nよく持ちかけられてます",
      "startTime": 138.966662693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.9666560332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……じゃあ、この話って……",
      "startTime": 140.9666560332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.8666560332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "詐欺の可能性が高いですね。この話に乗ろうものなら\n起業のための努力が全て無駄になってしまいますよ？",
      "startTime": 149.7999939918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.3333226998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、詐欺だって確定した訳じゃないでしょ！？\n幸運の女神は前髪しかないって言うじゃない！",
      "startTime": 157.4999939918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.9333226998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "今回は女神どころか悪魔ですよ、多分ですが\nまた、ロケ弁生活になってもいいんですか？",
      "startTime": 165.7333273251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "う。そ、それは……\n胃がもたれるし、肌にも悪いから絶対嫌ね……",
      "startTime": 172.2999939918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.3999863147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、詐欺かぁ……\nはぁ……そんなうまい話はないんですね……",
      "startTime": 182.2333263079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.7999863147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "franさんは実力がありますし、華もあります\n俺も頑張りますから。地道にいきましょう",
      "startTime": 190.7333263079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
